# Repo workspace extensibility

**Scope:** `REPO_ROOT`, `GET /repo/search`, `GET /repo/validate-range`, `pkgs/repo`, `repo_handlers.go`, `web/src/api/repo.ts`, and `web/src/tasks/extensions/*` (@ file picker / range UX). Task CRUD and SSE stay in **`13-tasks-stack-extensibility.mdc`**; this rule is for the read-only workspace slice and prompt mention validation that uses it.

**When to apply:** new or changed repo search/resolve rules, `/repo/*` behavior, JSON shapes for those routes, or web UI that calls `searchRepoFiles` / `validateRepoRange` or edits mention handling.

## Layering

1. **`pkgs/repo`** ‚Äî Path confinement under `Root`, search, line counting, `ValidatePromptMentions` / range checks. No HTTP; return errors (may wrap **`domain.ErrInvalidInput`** for bad user input). Keep limits (result caps, read sizes) here or document them in **`docs/DESIGN.md`**.
2. **`pkgs/tasks/handler/repo_handlers.go`** ‚Äî HTTP only: query params, status codes (503 when `h.repo == nil`, JSON error bodies per **`docs/DESIGN.md`**). Delegate to **`pkgs/repo`**; log and map failures consistently with existing handlers.
3. **`cmd/taskapi`** ‚Äî `repo.OpenRoot` when `REPO_ROOT` is set; pass `nil` into **`handler.NewHandler`** when unset (repo routes return 503).
4. **`web/src/api/repo.ts`** ‚Äî Sole place for `fetch` to `/repo/*`; parse `unknown` JSON defensively (same spirit as **`parseTaskApi`**).
5. **`web/src/tasks/extensions/`** ‚Äî Mention UI and hooks; no direct `fetch` for `/repo` (use **`repo.ts`**).

Prompt mention validation on **`POST /tasks`** / **`PATCH /tasks/{id}`** lives in the tasks handler + store path but calls **`pkgs/repo`**; changing mention syntax or validation rules usually touches **`pkgs/repo`** and task handler tests together‚Äîuse **`13-tasks-stack-extensibility.mdc`** for the task side and this rule for **`pkgs/repo`** and **`/repo/*`**.

## Contracts and docs

When routes, query params, or JSON fields change, follow **`11-api-contracts.mdc`** and update **`docs/DESIGN.md`** section **Optional workspace repo (`REPO_ROOT`)**.

## Tests

- **`pkgs/repo`:** table-driven tests; real temp dirs; no network.
- **Handler:** extend **`handler_http_test.go`** repo cases (`httptest`, temp repo root).
- **Web:** Vitest with mocked `fetch` for **`repo.ts`**; Testing Library for extensions (**`10-web-ui`**).

